dcterms:description: OpenAI Gym is a toolkit for developing and comparing reinforcement learning algorithms, providing a variety of environments to test and benchmark algorithms.
dcterms:title: OpenAI Gym

dcterms:description: CartPole-v1 is a classic control problem where the goal is to balance a pole on a cart by moving the cart left or right.
dcterms:title: CartPole-v1

dcterms:description: LunarLander-v2 is a reinforcement learning environment where the objective is to land a spacecraft on the lunar surface safely.
dcterms:title: LunarLander-v2

dcterms:description: MountainCar-v0 is a reinforcement learning environment where the goal is to drive a car up a steep hill, requiring the car to build momentum.
dcterms:title: MountainCar-v0

dcterms:description: Acrobot-v1 is a reinforcement learning environment where the goal is to swing a two-link robot arm to a certain height.
dcterms:title: Acrobot-v1
